# AVD-AWS-0104 — Unrestricted egress on Lambda security group
# Lambda functions require outbound internet access to reach AWS APIs and third-party endpoints.
AVD-AWS-0104

# AVD-AWS-0057 — IAM policy uses wildcard resource
# Resource ARNs are not known at plan time (dynamic bucket/table names).
# Scope will be tightened post-deployment using actual ARNs.
AVD-AWS-0057

# AVD-AWS-0011 — CloudFront WAF not enabled
# WAF is out of scope for this portfolio deployment. Can be added for production.
AVD-AWS-0011

# AVD-AWS-0190 — API Gateway stage access logging not configured
# Logging can be added post-deployment when a CloudWatch log group ARN is available.
AVD-AWS-0190

# AVD-AWS-0132 — S3 bucket not encrypted with customer managed key
# Using AWS-managed AES256 encryption. CMK adds cost/complexity not justified for this project.
AVD-AWS-0132

# AVD-AWS-0135 — SQS queue not encrypted with customer managed key
# Using AWS-managed SQS key. CMK adds cost/complexity not justified for this project.
AVD-AWS-0135
